Posts.Content: Jan 25, 2012 03:22PM just-wondering- wrote: Hi Mya.  Don't wait just do it.  Breast cancer does not wait.  Urgency is a must, not something to make you worry.  Size does not matter.  My breast cancer was so small and deep it did not show up on a mammogram.  Get an ultra-sound also.  Good luck and think positive.  Carla
